videos.description: Michigan State's Nick Ward gets the ball in the post and beats the double team to convert the hook lay-in.
videos.headline: Ward shakes off double team on hook layup

videos.description: After missing his initial shot attempt, Michigan State's Nick Ward grabs the offensive rebound and finishes the lay-in.
videos.headline: Ward converts second-chance bucket

videos.description: Michigan State's Matt McQuaid fakes the defender out on a pump fake and finds space to knock down an open jumper.
videos.headline: McQuaid's ball fake leads to easy jumper

videos.description: Michigan State's Lourawls Nairn Jr. finds Miles Bridges for the contested jump shot in the first half.
videos.headline: Bridges drains long jumper

videos.description: The "Izzone" dresses in teal to support the victims of the allegations ongoing at Michigan State.
videos.headline: 'Izzone' decked out in teal to support victims

videos.description: Michigan State's Cassius Winston gets the ball in transition and nails the contested lay-in.
videos.headline: Winston sinks tough transition layup

videos.description: With the shot clock running down, Michigan State's Miles Bridges pulls up behind the arc and sinks a tough 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bridges nails contested 3-pointer

videos.description: Wisconsin's Ethan Happ gets the ball in the post and converts a tough lay-in.
videos.headline: Happ finishes post lay-in

videos.description: Wisconsin's Ethan Happ tries to convert a layup in the paint but is rejected by Michigan State's Nick Ward.
videos.headline: Ward denies Happ inside

videos.description: Wisconsin's Ethan Happ tries sinking a post layup but is rejected by Michigan State's Jaren Jackson Jr.
videos.headline: Jackson swats Happ down low

videos.description: Michigan State's Lourawls Nairn Jr. swings the ball over to Cassius Winston behind the arc for an open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Winston extends Spartans' lead on open 3

videos.description: Wisconsin's Ethan Happ spins by Michigan State's Xavier Tillman in the post for a tough layup.
videos.headline: Happ spins by Tillman for post lay-in

videos.description: Wisconsin's Khalil Iverson spins by Michigan State's Miles Bridges to convert a tough layup, earning a trip to the line for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Iverson breezes by Bridges for and-1 chance

videos.description: Michigan State's Cassius Winston finds Jaren Jackson off the screen for an open 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Jackson converts 3 off pick-and-pop
